    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1509450/extras/be46169e8683b3dd627f83263a94e2e2.avif?t=1767296403\" width=600 height=80 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1509450/extras/a67b0b366b3671838c89f4523f47a704.poster.avif?t=1767296403\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1509450/extras/a67b0b366b3671838c89f4523f47a704.webm?t=1767296403\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1509450/extras/a67b0b366b3671838c89f4523f47a704.mp4?t=1767296403\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >分封制国家“万衍”在享用了数千年和平后走到了分崩离析的边缘，绵延数十个世代的战火让这片大地生灵涂炭。北方的军事强国——戮，百年间不断兼并邻国，成为万衍首屈一指的强大势力。南部新近成立的七国联盟则在盟主洪国的领导下与戮国对立，并极尽所能拉拢更多的国家加入联盟。游戏的主要舞台——帛国，则处于这两大势力的夹缝中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >帛国于十一年前被戮国突袭攻灭，旧帛国领为戮国占据。十一年后，大王子荒朱带着联盟的援军闪击旧帛国王都，并成功光复国家。然而这一场复国战争也许只是一系列混乱的开始……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《履云录》中，玩家将扮演帛国的中级指挥官，通过巧妙的排兵布阵和高超的指挥来帮助刚刚复国的帛国抵挡环伺强敌的侵攻。随着故事的深入，各方势力背后的野心和目的逐渐被你知晓和掌握。你又会何去何从呢？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3D的时刻制战棋游戏</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >抢先体验版超过20小时，完整版超过40小时的宏大故事</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >八名个性迥异，战斗风格也截然不同的队友</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>（实装40%）</i><strong>四十五种技能树</strong>，<strong>超过两百个不同技能</strong>随你搭配</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1509450/extras/ec299c628561f68ffa472d681e93b0dc.poster.avif?t=1767296403\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1509450/extras/ec299c628561f68ffa472d681e93b0dc.webm?t=1767296403\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1509450/extras/ec299c628561f68ffa472d681e93b0dc.mp4?t=1767296403\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>三十多名角色全动态立绘</strong>，四十余张全手绘场景图，大量剧情CG</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >力图描绘复杂的人际、势力关系网，构筑讲求逻辑的、稳健有说服力的世界观，只求认真仔细地讲好这个故事</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1509450/extras/a00ef2bc41c021f28afc198838941246.avif?t=1767296403\" width=600 height=80 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1509450/extras/092d9f2e4441a815dd27694d1ca5a6c5.poster.avif?t=1767296403\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1509450/extras/092d9f2e4441a815dd27694d1ca5a6c5.webm?t=1767296403\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1509450/extras/092d9f2e4441a815dd27694d1ca5a6c5.mp4?t=1767296403\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《履云录》采取独特的<strong>“策略值”</strong>系统。在角色的策略值耗尽前，<strong>角色可以任意移动和使用技能</strong>；但消耗的策略值越多，下一次行动的到来也会变得越慢。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >仔细控制行动次序条将是取胜的关键！通过巧妙的计算和排兵布阵来创造连续行动的窗口，并最终致胜。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可以通过放火和结冻地面来阻碍敌人的行动。占据有利地形，迎击来犯的敌人。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >复杂多变的标记系统。既有常态被动提升属性的一般标记，也有可以手动激发的战略用标记。巧妙运用这些标记，在战场上将再无“不可能”。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1509450/extras/9e116d307642e92c2dca84a5e9dd65db.avif?t=1767296403\" width=600 height=80 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1509450/extras/e19ff05dd95704ad5ab3a248a711557e.poster.avif?t=1767296403\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1509450/extras/e19ff05dd95704ad5ab3a248a711557e.webm?t=1767296403\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1509450/extras/e19ff05dd95704ad5ab3a248a711557e.mp4?t=1767296403\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过解锁技能树上的不同点位来改变主动技能的效果！同一个技能树上的技能可能效果完全不同。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>（待实装）</i>用合适的主动技能搭配合适的被动技能，以千变万化的队伍应对复杂的战局。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >数十种神兵利器亦或是日常生活品（？）供你收集，武装强化你的队伍。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1509450/extras/27d1aae02182d73d6b1e361d95a04f4b.avif?t=1767296403\" width=600 height=80 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1509450/extras/b7fc500638515ebcfd818604103aeccc.poster.avif?t=1767296403\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1509450/extras/b7fc500638515ebcfd818604103aeccc.webm?t=1767296403\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1509450/extras/b7fc500638515ebcfd818604103aeccc.mp4?t=1767296403\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >主线剧情间有自由活动时间，可以与队友约会，探索队友专属的支线剧情，或者干脆在练武场上演习练兵。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过自由活动时间的约会以及战场上出色的指挥，增加队友的好感度并解锁更多隐藏剧情。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >重要队友与你的好感度会决定是否能展开关键剧情，甚至决定结局。如果好感度过低，队友也可能会以各种方式离开你的身边。</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >真心对待你的队友：他们并不会天然地就对你感兴趣，更不会主动倒贴讨好你。友情从来都是讲求你来我往。</p></li></ul>",
